    "Clinical_Features": {
      "text": "Onset may range from hours to days\nSeizures\n, including\nstatus epilepticus\nEncephalopathy\n, ranging from mild\naltered mental status\nto\ncoma\nVisual disturbances\nHypertension\nNote that some proportion of patients may not exhibit significant hypertension; of note, a significant proportion of patients also had no known pre-existing hypertension\n[4]\nHeadache\n,\nvomiting\n, or other focal neurological deficits",
