    "Management": {
      "text": "Treat the underlying etiology\nControl Blood Pressure\n, considering gradual reduction to avoid sudden hypoperfusion\nDiscontinue immunosuppressants or cytotoxic medications\nStandard seizure management, if seizures are present\nIn cases related to\nPreeclampsia\nor\nHELLP syndrome\n, consider early OB/GYN consultation for delivery\n[6]",
